The paper deals with the problem of semantic image retrieval, which is a subfield of computer vision (cs.CV) and information retrieval (cs.IR). The use of word2vec embeddings and deep learning techniques suggests that the paper may also fall under the category of machine learning (cs.LG). Additionally, the paper deals with the processing of textual data (tags), which may also place it under the category of natural language processing (cs.CL). Finally, the use of image repositories and web data suggests that the paper may also fall under the category of multimedia (cs.MM).
